%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22Trump%20has%20a%20new%20plan%20to%20supercharge%20crypto%20markets%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223873%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22President%20Donald%20Trump%20raising%20his%20fist%20in%20the%20air%20while%20walking.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6847931b85e81483682bc03a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222617%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%26quot%3BWe%20had%20a%20good%20relationship%2C%20and%20I%20just%20wish%20him%20well.%20Very%20well%2C%20actually%2C%26quot%3B%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20said%20of%20Elon%20Musk%20on%20Monday.%3Cp%3ESaul%20Loeb%2FAFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ETrump%20has%20already%20been%20bullish%20for%20crypto%2C%20but%20he's%20got%20even%20more%20plans%20to%20boost%20the%20space.%20%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EA%20White%20House%20group%20revealed%20a%20policy%20plan%20to%20strengthen%20crypto%20markets%20this%20week.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20group's%20ideas%20involve%20establishing%20clearer%20rules%20around%20digital%20asset%20trading.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20dust%20is%20still%20settling%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcrypto-week-congress-stablecoins-genius-act-clarity-bitcoin-record-high-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecrypto%20week%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Capitol%20Hill%2C%20but%20government%20officials%20are%20already%20pushing%20their%20latest%20plan%20to%20boost%20digital%20assets.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Working%20Group%20on%20Digital%20Asset%20Markets%2C%20established%20under%20an%20order%20from%20President%20Donald%20Trump%2C%20released%20its%20report%20detailing%20crypto%20policy%20recommendations%20late%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFederal%20officials%20recommended%20that%20the%20US%20government%20establish%20a%20%26quot%3Bfit-for-purpose%20market%20structure%20framework%26quot%3B%20to%20best%20support%20the%20digital%20asset%20industry%20and%20help%20it%20grow%20while%20also%20protecting%20consumers%20and%20ensuring%20the%20US%20maintains%20its%20global%20crypto%20dominance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20White%20House%20fact%20sheet%20said%20that%20the%20group%20believes%20action%20is%20needed%20from%20both%20the%20Commodity%20Futures%20Trading%20Commission%20and%20the%20Securities%20and%20Exchange%20Commission%2C%20two%20agencies%20that%20have%20been%20at%20odds%20in%20the%20past%20over%20which%20one%20should%20regulate%20the%20sector.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20said%20that%20both%20regulatory%20agencies%20should%20use%20their%20authority%20to%20provide%20further%20clarity%20for%20investors%20around%20matters%20such%20as%20registration%2C%20custody%2C%20and%20trading.%20It%20also%20highlighted%20the%20need%20for%20the%20government%20to%20allow%20consumers%20access%20to%20%26quot%3Binnovative%20financial%20products%26quot%3B%20without%20certain%20regulatory%20or%20legal%20provisions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20group%20proposed%20that%20Congress%20enact%20legislation%20that%20%26quot%3Beliminates%20existing%20gaps%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fblockchain-cryptocurrency-regulations-us-global%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eregulatory%20oversight%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20providing%20the%20CFTC%20authority%20to%20oversee%20spot%20markets%20for%20non-security%20digital%20assets.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERegulatory%20clarity%20was%20a%20sticking%20point%20for%20the%20crypto%20market%20under%20past%20administrations.%20The%20SEC%20led%20by%20Gary%20Gensler%20during%20Joe%20Biden's%20term%20as%20president%20was%20often%20criticized%20by%20the%20market%20for%20not%20providing%20clear%20guidance%2C%20and%20for%20regulating%20by%20enforcement.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20market%20was%20already%20cheering%20this%20month's%20%26quot%3Bcrypto%20week%26quot%3B%20in%20Washington%2C%20and%20market%20players%20tell%20Business%20Insider%20that%20the%20latest%20policy%20proposals%20further%20strengthen%20government%20support%20for%20the%20space.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI've%20been%20building%20crypto%20infrastructure%20since%202017%20both%20for%20traditional%20entities%20and%20for%20DeFi%2C%20and%20%5Bthe%5D%20Working%20Group%20recommendations%20are%20the%20first%20time%20I've%20seen%20Washington%20actually%20understand%20what%20we%20need%2C%26quot%3B%20Connor%20Howe%2C%20co-founder%20of%20Enso.Build%2C%20told%20BI.%20%26quot%3BClear%20rules%2C%20not%20more%20enforcement.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EScott%20Buchanan%2C%20chief%20operating%20officer%20of%20Bitcoin%20Depot%2C%20also%20expressed%20optimism%20that%20new%20policies%20will%20help%20spur%20growth%20for%20crypto%20markets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BClear%20rules%20give%20the%20market%20confidence%2C%20open%20the%20door%20to%20mainstream%20adoption%2C%20and%20finally%20allow%20the%20industry%20to%20focus%20on%20growth%20instead%20of%20guessing%20what%20the%20rules%20are%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BWith%20a%20solid%20foundation%2C%20we%20could%20see%20reduced%20market%20volatility%20and%20a%20more%20stable%20environment%20for%20both%20retail%20and%20institutional%20investors.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20group%20released%20its%20report%2C%20several%20prominent%20cryptos%20have%20risen%2C%20including%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fcurrencies%2Fbtc-usd%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EBitcoin%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fcurrencies%2Feth-usd%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EEthereum%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fcurrencies%2Fsol-eur%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ESolana%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20indicating%20the%20market%20is%20reacting%20well%20to%20the%20news.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcrypto-white-house-policy-bitcoin-btc-genius-act-trump-2025-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C