0layoff%20happened%20around%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F2008%2F11%2Fsun-micro-firing-5-000-6-000-citing-new-economic-reality%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E2008%20at%20Sun%20Microsystems%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Starting%20in%202002%2C%20there%20were%20layoffs%20nearly%20every%20year%2C%20and%20I%20survived%20the%20first%20few.%20However%2C%20eventually%2C%20my%20group%20was%20hit%20pretty%20hard%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Foracel-buys-sun-microsystems-2009-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EOracle%20acquired%20the%20company%3C%2Fa%3E%20soon%20after.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20experienced%20three%20more%20layoffs%20after%20that.%20In%202019%2C%20I%20was%20one%20of%20the%20principal%20engineers%20laid%20off%20from%20a%20plagiarism-checker%20company.%20I%20was%20laid%20off%20again%20at%20the%20start%20of%20COVID%20by%20a%20different%20company%20because%20their%20revenues%20fell%20significantly%20in%20just%20one%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%20two%20months%20ago%2C%20I%20found%20out%20that%20my%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwalmart-cutting-roles-remove-layers-complexity-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eposition%20at%20Walmart%20Global%20Tech%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20a%20principal%20software%20engineer%20was%20being%20eliminated%20along%20with%20roughly%201%2C500%20other%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b11aed4c-2847-42ca-a9b6-63e04e611d65%5C%22%3EI%20don't%20think%20AI%20is%20the%20reason%20for%20software%20engineer%20layoffs%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAI%20has%20changed%20the%20job%20landscape%20in%20some%20ways%2C%20but%20I%20don't%20think%20it's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Foffice-paranoia-layoffs-ai-job-security-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecausing%20more%20layoffs%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20last%20couple%20of%20months%20of%20my%20job%2C%20Walmart%20started%20pushing%20everybody%20to%20start%20using%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%