er.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fbest-75-inch-tvs%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EBest%2075-inch%20TVs%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fbest-65-inch-tv%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EBest%2065-inch%20TVs%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fbest-55-inch-tvs%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EBest%2055-inch%20TVs%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fbest-50-inch-tvs%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EBest%2050-inch%20TVs%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Ch3%3EDoes%20LG%20make%208K%20TVs%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20LG%20has%20sold%208K%20TVs%20in%20the%20past%2C%20the%20brand%20does%20not%20currently%20have%20any%208K%20models%20in%20its%202025%20lineup.%20The%20only%20major%20brand%20with%20new%208K%20models%20this%20year%20is%20Samsung.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EAre%20LG%20TVs%20better%20than%20Samsung%20TVs%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3ELG%20and%20Samsung%20are%20both%20reliable%20brands%20that%20make%20several%20excellent%20TV%20models.%20In%20most%20respects%2C%20it's%20hard%20to%20say%20that%20one%20is%20definitively%20better%20than%20the%20other.%20Instead%2C%20they%20each%20have%20certain%20strengths%20and%20weaknesses%20across%20their%20lineups%2C%20depending%20on%20your%20viewing%20needs%20and%20which%20models%20you're%20considering.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELG%20was%20the%20first%20TV%20brand%20to%20bring%204K%20OLED%20displays%20to%20the%20mass%20market%2C%20and%20it%20offers%20a%20comprehensive%20collection%20of%20OLED%20models%20in%20many%20sizes.%20Meanwhile%2C%20Samsung%20entered%20the%204K%20OLED%20market%20much%20later%20and%20initially%20had%20a%20more%20limited%20lineup.%20This%20has%20started%20to%20change%20in%20the%20last%20two%20years%2C%20though%2C%20and%20now%20Samsung%20offers%20a%20similar%20selection%20of%20sizes%20and%20performance%20tiers.%20However%2C%20LG%20is%20still%20the%20only%20brand%20that%20sells%20a%2097-inch%20OLED.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBoth%20companies%20use%20WOLED%20panels%20in%20some%20of%20their%20models%2C%20while%20Samsung%20also%20uses%20QD-OLED%20screens%20in%20certain%20sizes.%20QD-OLED%20panels%20have%20an%20edge%20in%20color%20and%20brightness%2C%20but%20WOLED%20panels%20offer%20deeper%20black%20levels%20in%20rooms%20with%20ambient%20light.%20LG%20uses%20a%20four-stack%20OLED%20panel%20in%20its%20high-end%20G5%20OLED%2C%20which%20exceeds%20the%20brightness%20of%20Samsung's%20QD-OLEDs%20and%20better%20competes%20with%20their%20color%20performance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBoth%20companies%20also%20sell%20LCD-based%20TVs%2C%20with%20entry-level%20options%20that%20use%20standard%20LED%20panels%20and%20more%20advanced%20models%20with%20QLED%20screens%2C%20local%20dimming%2C%20and%20Mini%20LED%20backlights.%20LG%20brands%20its%20more%20advanced%20LCD%20TVs%20as%20QNED%20and%20NanoCell%2C%20while%20Samsung%20brands%20its%20high-end%20LCD%20TVs%20as%20Neo%20QLED.%20Though%20some%20of%20LG's%20newest%20QNED%20TVs%20have%20gotten%20a%20lot%20better%20than%20past%20models%2C%20generally%20speaking%2C%20Samsung's%20Neo%20QLEDs%20offer%20better%20backlight%20control.%20Check%20out%20our%20guide%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fbest-samsung-tvs%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebest%20Samsung%20TVs%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20see%20our%20top%20picks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELG%20and%20Samsung%20both%20use%20their%20own%20proprietary%20smart%20TV%20interfaces%2C%20and%20they%20both%20support%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fxbox-game-pass%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EXbox%20Game%20Pass%3C%2Fa%3E%20streaming%20and%20similar%20AI%20functions.%20That%20said%2C%20LG's%20remotes%20stand%20out%20with%20motion%20controls%2C%20and%20Samsung's%20remotes%20stand%20out%20with%20SolarCell%20technology%20that%20works%20without%20a%20battery.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20important%20distinction%20between%20the%20two%20brands%20is%20that%20LG%20supports%20Dolby%20Vision%20HDR%20on%20its%20mid-%20and%20high-end%20TVs%2C%20while%20Samsung%20supports%20the%20competing%20HDR10%2B%20format.%20These%20formats%20provide%20similar%20performance%2C%20but%20Dolby%20Vision%20content%20is%20more%20widespread%20across%20streaming%20services%20and%204K%20Blu-ray%20discs.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EShould%20you%20worry%20about%20burn-in%20on%20an%20LG%20TV%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3ELG%20TVs%20branded%20as%20LED%2C%20NanoCell%2C%20and%20QNED%20are%20not%20susceptible%20to%20burn-in.%20However%2C%20LG's%20OLED%20TVs%20are%20technically%20capable%20of%20burn-in%20in%20extreme%20situations.%20That%20said%2C%20burn-in%20is%20rare%20under%20typical%20viewing%20conditions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBurn-in%20is%20an%20issue%20that%20can%20occur%20if%20you%20leave%20a%20static%20image%20on%20an%20OLED%20TV%20for%20too%20long%2C%20such%20as%20the%20CNN%20or%20ESPN%20logo%20in%20the%20corner%20of%20the%20screen.%20When%20burn-in%20happens%2C%20a%20faint%20afterimage%20gets%20stuck%20on%20the%20display.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20shoppers%20should%20be%20aware%20of%20this%20risk%2C%20LG%20OLED%20TVs%20have%20features%20designed%20to%20prevent%20burn-in%2C%20including%20%3Cspan%3Epixel%20refreshers%2C%20logo%20dimmers%2C%20and%20automatic%20pixel%20shift%20modes.%20Websites%20like%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rtings.com%2Ftv%2Ftests%2Flongevity-burn-in-test-updates-and-results%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cu%3ERtings%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0have%20conducted%20long-term%20burn-in%20tests%20with%20OLEDs%2C%20including%20LG%20models%2C%20and%20though%20its%20results%3C%2Fspan%3E%20show%20that%20burn-in%20can%20occur%2C%20it%20requires%20specific%20circumstances%20that%20don't%20apply%20to%20average%20use%20cases.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20owned%20an%20LG%20OLED%20for%20more%20than%20three%20years%20and%20never%20saw%20any%20sig