ning%20about%20famous%20places.%3Cp%3Eor%20dzongs%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20guide%20had%20been%20a%20trekking%20and%20cultural%20guide%20for%20more%20than%2030%20years%2C%20so%20his%20understanding%20of%20the%20history%2C%20culture%2C%20and%20natural%20environment%20of%20Bhutan%20was%20unbelievable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20hit%20him%20with%20every%20question%20imaginable%2C%20and%20he%20never%20faltered.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhether%20talking%20about%20the%20government%20philosophy%20of%20Gross%20National%20Happiness%2C%20the%20history%20of%20Tiger's%20Nest%20monastery%2C%20or%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcaterpillar-fungus-expensive-most-valuable-parasite-2019-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ehow%20to%20find%20cordyceps%3C%2Fa%3E%20(a%20valuable%20fungi%20some%20locals%20collect)%2C%20the%20man%20knew%20his%20stuff.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHaving%20a%20human%20encyclopedia%20on%20hand%20was%20handy%20and%20made%20each%20stop%20far%20more%20interesting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20translated%20for%20us%20while%20we%20were%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbefriended-older-airbnb-hosts-changed-my-perspective-life-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Estaying%20with%20host%20families%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20remote%20locations.%20This%20allowed%20us%20to%20connect%20with%20the%20locals%20on%20a%20deeper%20level%2C%20which%20definitely%20enriched%20our%20experience.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20many%20ways%2C%20he%20just%20made%20our%20trip%20easier.%20It%20was%20incredibly%20convenient%20having%20someone%20else%20take%20care%20of%20the%20finer%20travel%20details%2C%20like%20where%20we%20were%20staying%20and%20how%20we'd%20get%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDoing%20an%20organized%20tour%20meant%20I%20could%20kick%20back%20and%20relax%20while%20someone%20else%20was%20at%20the%20helm.%20By%20the%20end%20of%20the%20trip%2C%20I%20definitely%20felt%20recharged.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2294a6a