ic-beach-access-information%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERent%20Siesta%20Key%3C%2Fa%3E.%20However%2C%20they%20often%20fill%20up%20by%20mid-morning%2C%20which%20I%20noticed%20when%20I%20was%20leaving.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20beach%20has%20unique%20sand%20that%20stays%20cool%20to%20the%20touch%20even%20in%20scorching%20temperatures.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222400%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22people%20on%20the%20beach%20at%20siesta%20key%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F688a3b6d3d5881a51c1e442d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20sand%20in%20Siesta%20Key%20is%20made%20up%20almost%20entirely%20of%20eroded%20Appalachian%20quartz.%3Cp%3EKristine%20Villarroel%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMade%20up%20almost%20entirely%20of%20pure%20quartz%2C%20the%20white%20powdery%20sand%20on%20Siesta%20Key's%20shores%20traveled%20down%20from%20the%20Appalachian%20Mountains%2C%20getting%20eroded%20into%20tiny%20sand%20particles%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsiestasand.us%2Fsarasota-history-01-19%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESiesta%20Sand%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20sand's%20unique%20composition%20keeps%20it%20cool%20to%20the%20touch%20even%20under%20the%20scorching%20Florida%20sun%2C%20one%20of%20the%20main%20reasons%20the%20beach%20is%20ranked%20at%20the%20top%20of%20the%20national%20rankings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20feeling%20this%20unique%20sand%20was%20an%20experience%20of%20its%20own.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnlike%20the%20strenuous%20beach%20days%20of%20my%20childhood%2C%20where%20you'd%20have%20to%20sprint%20from%20the%20car%20to%20the%20water%20to%20keep%20the%20hot%20sand%20from%20burning%20your%20feet%2C%20walking%20on%20Siesta%20Key's%20quartz%20sand%20was%20relaxing%2C%20even%20while%20standing%20under%20the%20bright%20Florida%20sun.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EEach%20year%2C%20the%20beach's%20unique%