a.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Fseed-preservation-Darlapudi-Ravi-1-1732015622-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Fseed-preservation-Darlapudi-Ravi-1-1732015622-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Fseed-preservation-Darlapudi-Ravi-1-1732015622-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Fseed-preservation-Darlapudi-Ravi-1-1732015622-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-381108%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EWhile%20genetically%20modified%20seeds%20are%20known%20for%20their%20quantity%20of%20fruiting%2C%20these%20lack%20nutrients%2C%20Darlapudi%20discovered.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20aside%20from%20teaching%20him%20the%20nuances%20of%20green%20farming%20practices%2C%20the%20course%20also%20fuelled%20his%20interest%20in%20the%20ethnoscience%20of%20seeds.%C2%A0%20He%20ventured%20into%20the%20jungles%20of%20Dantewada%20in%20Chhattisgarh%2C%C2%A0to%20collect%20sample%20seed%20varieties%20grown%20by%20the%20tribal%20communities%20in%20the%20region.%20These%20held%20a%20special%20draw.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThese%20days%2C%20chemical%20fertilisers%20and%20pesticides%20are%20used%20in%20agriculture.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20the%20seeds%20get%20diversified%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%20But%20in%20these%20tribal%20areas%2C%20he%20found%20the%20seeds%20to%20be%20untouched%20by%20chemicals.%20From%20a%20passion%20trip%2C%20this%20spiralled%20into%20a%20project%20that%20has%20now%20been%20running%20for%20almost%20a%20decade.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%E2%80%99s%20not%20all%2C%20he%20shares.%20%E2%80%9CI%20have%20also%20followed%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F255272%2Fnekram-sharma-nau-anaj-intercropping-system-himachal-pradesh-mandi-traditional