%99t%20help%20but%20smile%20at%20this%20%E2%80%98pinch-me%E2%80%99%20moment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERight%20from%20the%20outset%2C%20Khanna%20is%20chipper%3B%20no%20one%20(except%20probably%20the%20general%20manager%20at%20%E2%80%98Bungalow%E2%80%99%2C%20Sameer%20Bhatt)%20would%20guess%20he%20has%20pulled%20an%20all-nighter.%20Well%20into%20the%20wee%20hours%20of%20the%20morning%2C%20Khanna%20was%20attempting%20to%20replicate%20the%20intricate%20wings%20of%20a%20peacock%E2%80%99s%20feathers%20onto%20the%20surface%20of%20a%20piece%20of%20coconut%20%3Cem%3Ebarfi%3C%2Fem%3E%20(Indian%20sweet).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFour%20decades%20of%20culinary%20experience%20ensured%20he%20aced%20the%20task.%20And%20now%20for%20replicating%20the%20same%20onto%20a%20hundred-odd%20pieces!%20Known%20to%20push%20the%20envelope%2C%20Khanna%20does%20justice%20to%20this%20reputation%20when%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20wanted%20each%20feather%20to%20be%20exactly%20alike.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharing%20how%20the%20plumage%20was%20meant%20to%20be%20reminiscent%20of%20the%20%3Cem%3Emandirs%20%3C%2Fem%3E(temples)%20in%20Indian%20homes%2C%20Khanna%20was%20keen%20that%20every%20guest%20at%20%E2%80%98Bungalow%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%94%20his%20dream%20restaurant%20project%20launched%20in%20New%20York%20in%20March%20this%20year%20%E2%80%94%20return%20home%20that%20day%20with%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F288997%2Fpunjabi-wrestler-harbans-vig-invented-indias-loved-dhodha-barfi-history%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebox%20of%20coconut%20%3Cem%3Ebarfi%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20spot%20the%20delicate%20%3Cem%3Emor%20pankh%3C%2Fem%3E%20(peacock%20feather)%2C%20and%20smile.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fvikas-khanna-12-1729605875.jpg%5