Their%20collaborators%20include%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-list%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Bakul%20Foundation%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20a%20volunteer-driven%20movement%20in%20Odisha%20enabling%20public%20initiatives%20like%20free%20libraries%20and%20art%20programmes.%3Cbr%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ESambad%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20a%20major%20Odia%20news%20outlet.%3Cbr%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EGoonj%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20a%20humanitarian%20organisation%20working%20on%20disaster%20relief%20and%20rural%20development.%3Cbr%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ESELCO%20Foundation%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20which%20develops%20decentralised%20renewable%20energy-based%20solutions.%3Cbr%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20new%20way%20to%20talk%20about%20the%20weather%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Socratus%20began%20looking%20for%20a%20place%20to%20test%20its%20ideas%2C%20Odisha%20felt%20like%20the%20obvious%20choice.%20The%20state%20lives%20under%20the%20constant%20threat%20of%20cyclones%20and%20floods.%20Its%20landscapes%20%E2%80%94%20from%20dense%20forests%20to%20fragile%20coastlines%20%E2%80%94%20are%20among%20the%20most%20vulnerable%20to%20climate%20change.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOdisha%20also%20had%20a%20strong%20base%20to%20build%20on.%20It%20was%20the%20first%20Indian%20state%20to%20adopt%20a%20comprehensive%20climate%20action%20plan%2C%20with%20systems%20stretching%20from%20the%20grassroots%20to%20the%20state%20level.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJust%20as%20important%20are%20the%20people.%20Nearly%2023%20percent%20of%20Odisha%E2%80%99s%20population%20belongs%20to%2064%20Scheduled%20Tribes.%20Twelve%20out%20of%20its%2030%20districts%20are%20tribal-dominated%2C%20home%20to%20communities%20living%20across%20forests%2C%20wetlands%2C%20farmlands%2C%20and%20coastal%20belts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20bring%20its%20philosophy%20to%20life%2C%20Socratus%20teamed%20up%20with%20organisations%20like%20Sambad%20and%2