.com%2F447032%2Fshyam-sunder-jyani-teacher-turned-environmentalist-restored-mining-wasteland-in-rajasthan-with-community-support%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20reservoirs%20%3C%2Fa%3Eare%20made%20with%20embankments%20on%20three%20sides%20that%20are%20situated%20at%20the%20end%20of%20diversion%20channels.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20diversion%20channels%20known%20as%20pynes%20are%20artificial%20rivulets%20that%20are%20extended%20from%20rivers%20to%20collect%20water%20and%20channel%20it%20to%20the%20Ahars%20for%20irrigation%20during%20dry%20months.%20In%20a%20state%20that%20is%20largely%20known%20for%20its%20agricultural%20contribution%2C%20especially%20paddy%20cultivation%2C%20this%20technique%20of%20using%20Ahar%20Pynes%20is%20exceptionally%20useful%20in%20low-rainfall%20areas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EApatani%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%20wp-image-280154%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F03%2Fwater-1-1648034024.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Apatani%20is%20used%20in%20the%20rural%20Arunachal%20Pradesh%20for%20wet%20rice%20cultivation%20and%20fish%20farming.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F03%2Fwater-1-1648034024.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F03%2Fwater-1-1648034024-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F03%2Fwater-1-1648034024-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F03%2Fwater-1-1648034024-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F03%2Fwater-1-1648034024-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-280154%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3