rdeners%2C%20a%20common%20concern%20arises%20when%20they%20go%20on%20a%20vacation%20or%20a%20mandatory%20work%20trip%2C%20leaving%20their%20plants%20at%20the%20mercy%20of%20nature.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnfortunately%2C%20all%20the%20hard%20work%20invested%20in%20the%20garden%20can%20be%20in%20vain%20when%20they%20return%20to%20find%20withering%20or%20near-dying%20plants.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHyderabad-based%20Gowtham%20Reddy%20was%20motivated%20to%20solve%20this%20universal%20problem.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20may%20not%20appear%20as%20a%20serious%20issue%20for%20many%2C%20but%20it%20keeps%20many%20gardeners%20anxious.%20We%20cannot%20ignore%20any%20problem%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20speaking%20to%20gardeners%20and%20exploring%20several%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F284070%2Fself-watering-plant-care-technique-tricks-gardening-hacks-summer-heat%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDIY%20drip%20systems%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Gowtham%20worked%20on%20the%20simplest%20self-watering%20system%20called%20%E2%80%98Osmos%E2%80%99%20that%20can%20sustain%20plants%20for%20at%20least%2015%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FGowtham-Reddy-2-1700051890.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FGowtham-Reddy-2-1700051890.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FGowtham-Reddy-2-1700051890-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FGowtham-Reddy-2-1700051890-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FGowtham-Reddy-2-1700051890-768x402.jpg%20