ing%20programmes%20involving%20%3Cstrong%3Esolar-powered%20cold%20storages%20and%20dryers%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAfter%20our%20mapping%20exercise%2C%20we%20found%20that%20some%20of%20these%20funds%20can%20be%20tapped%20for%20smallholder%20farmers.%20At%20the%20time%2C%20the%20Directorate%20of%20Horticulture%20was%20actually%20leading%20a%20lot%20of%20programmes%20on%20solar-powered%20cold%20storages%20and%20dryers%20for%20farmers.%20We%20felt%20that%20if%20we%20could%20kind%20of%20mobilise%20this%20fund%2C%20then%20we%20would%20be%20able%20to%20procure%20these%20products%20on%20behalf%20of%20the%20department%20and%20distribute%20them%20to%20farmer%20producer%20organisations%20(FPOs).%20For%20the%20first%20cycle%20of%20procurement%2C%20we%20included%20a%20buyback%20clause%2C%20i.e.%20the%20vendor%20selling%20the%20equipment%20is%20also%20responsible%20for%20buying%20the%20first%20cycle%20of%20produce%20harvested%20by%20farmers%20in%20these%20FPOs%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Gaurav.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20clause%20aimed%20to%20incentivise%20the%20adoption%20of%20solar%20drying%20technology%20and%20ensure%20early%20returns%20for%20farmers.%20Starting%20with%20%3Cstrong%3ERamgarh%20and%20Bokaro%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20the%20model%20soon%20expanded%20to%20%3Cstrong%3EDumka%2C%20Chaibasa%2C%20Latehar%2C%20and%20Chatra%3C%2Fstrong%3E%E2%80%94the%20latter%20emerging%20as%20the%20most%20successful%20district%20in%20mobilising%20public%20funds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Ffeatured-img-4_11zon-1753712413.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Solar%20dryers%20with%20buyback%20guarantees%20helped%20farmers%20adopt%20technology%20and%20secure%20early%20profits.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Ffeatured-i