rom%20the%20date%20of%20releasing%20the%20expression%20of%20interest%20to%20finding%20adequate%20vendors%2C%20to%20changing%20the%20RFP%20policy%20and%20then%20finally%20doing%20the%20demonstration.%20Although%20willingness%20and%20resources%20were%20often%20available%2C%20our%20program%20delivery%20designs%20tended%20to%20be%20overly%20complex%20and%20to%20cause%20delays%20in%20funding.%20The%20year%202020%E2%80%9321%20was%20spent%20on%20getting%20these%20dryers%20and%20cold%20storages%20out%2C%20followed%20by%20six%20months%20of%20demonstrations%20from%20private%20vendors%20to%20FPOs%2C%20showing%20farmers%20how%20to%20use%20this%20equipment%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Gaurav.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20part%20of%20the%20implementation%2C%20farmers%20were%20trained%20to%20use%20the%20new%20technology.%20%3Cstrong%3EAbdul%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20a%2024-year-old%20farmer%20from%20Latehar%2C%20recalls%2C%20%E2%80%9CInitially%2C%20we%20received%20a%20few%20training%20sessions%20on%20how%20to%20use%20the%20solar%20dryer%20and%20how%20to%20cut%20tomatoes.%20During%20the%20installation%20phase%2C%20they%20also%20provided%20extensive%20training%20on%20each%20part%20and%20how%20to%20use%20it%20correctly.%E2%80%9D%20Two%20private%20vendors%20were%20ultimately%20chosen%20to%20supply%20the%20solar%20equipment%20after%20a%20rigorous%20selection%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20designed%20the%20technical%20eligibility%20criteria%20to%20determine%20which%20vendors%20we%20would%20use%20to%20distribute%20this%20solar%20equipment%2C%20which%20included%20having%20experience%20working%20with%20at%20least%2010%20FPOs%20and%20implementing%20five%20social%20programmes%2C%20among%20others.%20We%20started%20with%2011%20vendors%20putting%20in%20their%20bids%2C%20but%20eventually%20only%20two%20were%20left%20standing%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Gaurav.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20s