%20and%20everything%20depends%20on%20mining%20today.%20See%2C%20these%20mines%20will%20close%20one%20day.%20Some%20of%20the%20mines%20will%20get%20shut%20down%20because%20the%20government%20is%20trying%20to%20promote%20renewable%20solutions.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhat%20would%20then%20happen%20with%20these%20entire%20sets%20of%20workers%3F%20Are%20they%20skilled%20enough%20to%20take%20up%20alternate%20work%3F%20That%20is%20why%20a%20part%20of%20the%20JH-RESET%20project%20is%20also%20to%20train%20the%20people%20on%20using%20solar%20dryers%2C%20solar%20pumps%2Firrigation%20systems%20or%20become%20solar%20entrepreneurs.%20The%20base%20of%20this%20programme%20has%20always%20been%20to%20increase%20the%20economic%20value%20of%20stakeholders%20like%20smallholder%20farmers%2C%20but%20it%20is%20built%20on%20solutions%20which%20come%20in%20the%20renewable%20area.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FWS-Poster-640-x-853_11zon-1753712938-500x666.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22From%20farming%20to%20floriculture%2C%20JH-RESET%20is%20opening%20clean%2C%20profitable%20livelihood%20options%20for%20mining%20communities.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FWS-Poster-640-x-853_11zon-1753712938-500x666.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FWS-Poster-640-x-853_11zon-1753712938-225x300.jpg%20225w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FWS-Poster-640-x-853_11zon-1753712938-600x800.jpg%20600w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FWS-Poster-640-x-853_11zon-1753712938-450x600.jpg%20450w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FWS-Poster-640-x-853_11zo