Department%20to%20connect%20job%20seekers%20with%20online%20certification%2C%20government%20schemes%2C%20and%20sector-specific%20training.%3Cbr%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EInterdepartmental%20Coordination%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%3Cbr%3EEmployment%20exchanges%20can%20act%20as%20intermediaries%20to%20help%20employers%20navigate%20permits%2C%20licenses%2C%20and%20access%20to%20subsidies%20by%20coordinating%20across%20government%20departments%E2%80%94making%20the%20process%20less%20fragmented.%3Cbr%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EDatabase%20of%20Informal%20Workers%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%3Cbr%3EEstablishing%20a%20digital%20registry%20of%20informal%20workers%2C%20especially%20in%20sectors%20like%20waste%20management%2C%20is%20essential%20for%20transitioning%20them%20into%20formal%2C%20stable%20employment.%3Cbr%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20road%20ahead%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20of%202023%E2%80%9324%2C%20the%20exact%20number%20of%20green%20jobs%20created%20through%20Jharkhand%E2%80%99s%20employment%20exchanges%2C%20in%20partnership%20with%20the%20Swaniti%20Initiative%20and%20other%20agencies%2C%20has%20not%20been%20publicly%20disclosed.%20However%2C%20green%20jobs%20are%20now%20being%20listed%20on%20the%20State%E2%80%99s%20official%20employment%20portal%E2%80%94indicating%20that%20institutional%20mechanisms%20are%20being%20put%20in%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20these%20early%20steps%2C%20significant%20work%20remains.%20For%20a%20state%20deeply%20reliant%20on%20coal%20and%20informal%20labour%2C%20a%20deliberate%20and%20well-resourced%20strategy%20is%20required%20to%20ensure%20that%20workers%20aren%E2%80%99t%20left%20behind%20in%20India%E2%80%99s%20green%20transition.%20The%20future%20of%20Jharkhand%E2%80%99s%20workforce%E2%80%94and%20its%20equitable%20development%E2%80%94depends%20on%20getting%20this%20transition%20right.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1753713908000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-med