20valley%20beyond.%20Haripriya%2C%20a%20technical%20manager%20at%20a%20corporate%20firm%2C%20says%20the%20intent%20was%20to%20lease%20the%20place%20out%20when%20it%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20being%20occupied%20by%20them.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20homestay%20is%20surrounded%20by%20a%20thick%20cover%20of%20large%20trees%20and%20lush%20green%20vegetation.%20The%20idea%20was%20to%20have%20three%20ethnic%20fusion%20houses%20that%20blend%20ancient%20looks%20from%20the%20outside%20with%20vernacular%20architecture%20on%20the%20inside%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20pictures%20suggest%2C%20the%20architecture%20here%20really%20casts%20spells%20like%20a%20fairytale.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201715px)%20100vw%2C%201715px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F1_11zon-1697108367.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221715%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20farmhouses%20on%20the%20Bannerghatta%20property%20are%20made%20with%20mud%20and%20stone%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F1_11zon-1697108367.jpg%201715w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F1_11zon-1697108367-300x200.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F1_11zon-1697108367-500x333.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F1_11zon-1697108367-768x512.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F1_11zon-1697108367-1536x1024.jpg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F1_11zon-1697108367-150x100.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-332069%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221143%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20farmhouses%20on%20the%20Bannerghatta%20property%20are%20made%20with%20mud%20and%20stone%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Anirudh%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBreathing%20life%20into%20a%20deserted%20land%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20decision%20to%20entrust%20the%20project%20to%20Anirudh%20was%20backed%20by%20the%20success%20of%20his%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F328878%2Fcouple-builds-saroga-woods-carbon-friendly-solar-powered-sustainable-homestay-in-himachal%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eprevious%20projects%3C%2Fa%3E%20which%20are%20rooted%20in%20sustainability.%20Building%20mud%20homes%20are%20Anirudh%E2%80%99s%20forte%2C%20the%20three%20discovered.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVijayaprabhu%2C%20who%20has%20a%20background%20in%20the%20pharmaceutical%20industry%2C%20shares%20that%20the%20decision%20to%20invest%20in%20this%20specific%20location%20was%20followed%20by%20a%20conscious%20choice%20to%20opt%20for%20sustainable%20construction.%20%E2%80%9CWhile%20we%20were%20looking%20for%20options%2C%20we%20came%20across%20vernacular%20architecture%20through%20our%20common%20friend%20and%20found%20it%20interesting.%20We%20spent%20time%20understanding%20the%20process%20of%20this%20construction%20and%20decided%20it%20was%20the%20right%20one%20to%20go%20ahead%20with.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Vijayaprabhu%20and%20Haripriya%20opted%20for%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F328655%2Fsunnymead-eco-friendly-earthquake-resistant-homestay-in-shimla-built-with-dhajji-dewari-architecture%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emud%20construction%3C%2Fa%3E%20based%20on%20intrigue%2C%20to%20Revathi%20it%20held%20a%20personal%20allure.%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20born%20in%20a%20mud%20home%20in%20my%20native%20village%20and%20always%20wanted%20to%20go%20back%20to%20my%20roots.%20Mud%20houses%20have%20a%20direct%20connection%20with%20nature%20and%20induce%20a%20natural%20living%20experience.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnirudh%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20was%20more%20than%20happy%20to%20take%20it%20on.%20Designing%20a%20farm%20stay%20on%20the%20outskirts%20of%20a%20forest%20is%20not%20a%20project%20one%20comes%20across%20every%20day.%20As%20he%20describes%20the%20features%20of%20the%20farm%20stay%20spread%20across%20the%20four-acre%20land%2C%20one%20can%20tell%20how%20seamlessly%20the%20raw%20finesse%20of%20the%20property%20blends%20into%20the%20surrounding%20foliage.%20A%20process%20that%20lasted%20over%20two%20years%20saw%20the%20light%20of%20day%20six%20months%20ago%20when%20Anirudh%20handed%20the%20keys%20over%20to%20the%20trio.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharing%20his%20design%20philosophy%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThey%20were%20looking%20for%20a%20typical%20South%20Indian%20traditional%20home%20with%20a%20courtyard%20that%20would%20wrap%20itself%20around%20the%20front%20of%20the%20house.%20The%20courtyard%20would%20be%20a%20communal%20sit-out%20area%20where%20they%20could%20relax%20in%20the%20evenings%20and%20enjoy%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F327701%2Fcouple-restores-woodway-estate-british-era-home-into-heritage-homestay-in-chikmagalur%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eglorious%20view%20of%20the%20farmland%3C%2Fa%3E%20overlooking%20the%20valley.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20friends%20insisted%20on%20an%20open-plan%20system%20with%20as%20few%20walls%20as%20possible.%20So%2C%20Anirudh%20shares%20that%20while%20the%20bedrooms%20and%20toilets%20are%20enclosed%2C%20the%20living%20room%2C%20dining%20room%20and%20kitchen%20spaces%20are%20continuous.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20entire%20property%20has%20been%20built%20keeping%20mud%20as%20the%20hero%20element%2C%20with%20stone%20filling%20in%20the%20spaces.%20What%20this%20does%20aside%20from%20being%20an%20aesthetic%20addition%20is%20that%20it%20breaks%20the%20monotony%20of%20the%20